   <description url="http://code.google.com/p/hits/">
      HiTS - High Throughput Screening
KNIME plugin for analysing data from HTS/HCS experiments using
cellHTS2 (based on 2.8.2, but should work well with 2.8.3 too).
It depends on Rserve.
It also supports basic data visualisation technics, like heatmaps. (For a bit more advanced visualisation check: KNIME labs, and the ie.tcd.imm.hits.exp.feature feature.)
News in version 0.4.0:
 - bug fixes,
 - improved colour legend export
 - more detailed error messages
 - new node:
   - Score to P value
   </description>

